<ul>
<li><a href="https://stackoverflow.com/q/7977945/1366033">HTML-parser on Node.js</a></li>
<li><a href="https://stackoverflow.com/q/7372972/1366033">How do I parse a HTML page with Node.js</a></li>
</ul>
